[p 
	[em 
		"Phantasy Star IV
	]em
	", released in Japan as 
	[em 
		"Phantasy Star: The End of the Millennium
	]em
	", is a role-playing video game released for the Mega Drive/Genesis in Japan in 1993 and Europe and North America in 1995. It is the fourth and final game in the original 
	[em 
		"Phantasy Star
	]em
	" series, concluding the story of the Algol Star System. 
	[em 
		"Phantasy Star IV
	]em
	" kept many of the gameplay elements of the previous game, including turn-based battles, overhead exploration, and magic spells. It received mixed reviews upon its release, but has been subject to positive critical retrospectives.
	$LF
